snippet: Johnny Damon was 2 for 4 with a run scored, but his Thailand team was eliminated from the Classic qualifying by New Zealand, 12-2, in eight innings.
abstract: New Zealand defeats Thailand, 12-2, eliminating team, and outfielder Johnny Damon, from World Baseball Classic qualifying.
lead_paragraph: Johnny Damon was 2 for 4 with a run scored, but his Thailand team was eliminated from the Classic qualifying by New Zealand, 12-2, in eight innings.
